{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>About the Game</strong></h2><br>Separated from his sled team by an avalanche, you must guide Brutus, the Siberian Husky, through the Alaskan wilderness \u2013 across lakes, cliffsides, and caverns, to rejoin his team and continue their mission to deliver lifesaving medicine to the people of Nome, Alaska. Avoid succumbing to the harsh environment as you explore and overcome puzzles and obstacles in <i>Lost Beacon</i>.<br><br><strong>Interaction</strong><br><br>Move obstacles and bound across crumbling platforms to bypass ravines, chasms, lakes, and glacial barriers. <br><br><strong>Exploration</strong><br><br>Explore a scenic open-world landscape as you search for your pack. Jump from ledges and across chasms to investigate new areas and uncover lost secrets.<br><br><strong>Uncover History</strong><br><br>Guided by your powerful sense of smell and the benevolent forest spirit, Silla, recover lost journals recounting the history of the Iditarod Trail and sled dogs. While searching for your team, learn about the Alaskan Diphtheria Outbreak and the 1925 Serum Run to Nome.","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"What a beautiful day","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2440210/541c4b0e1672e06ae52046a82e6bda9b836972fc.jpg"},{"name":"Dashing through the snow!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2440210/541c4b0e1672e06ae52046a82e6bda9b836972fc.jpg"},{"name":"Go get it boy!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2440210/541c4b0e1672e06ae52046a82e6bda9b836972fc.jpg"},{"name":"Woof Woof!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2440210/541c4b0e1672e06ae52046a82e6bda9b836972fc.jpg"},{"name":"Big Dog!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2440210/541c4b0e1672e06ae52046a82e6bda9b836972fc.jpg"},{"name":"It's getting late Brutis","path":"